---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<section
  class="relative w-full min-h-[70vh] md:h-[80vh] overflow-hidden"
  style="font-family: 'Noto Serif Variable', serif;"
>
  <!-- Imagen de fondo -->
  <Image
    src="https://img.freepik.com/fotos-premium/primer-plano-postre-servido-mesa-contra-fondo-negro_1609942-1549.jpg?semt=ais_hybrid&w=740&q=80"
    alt="Hero"
    width={1920}
    height={1080}
    loading="eager"
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover animate-slow-zoom"
  />

  <!-- Overlay oscuro -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/60"></div>

  <!-- Contenido centrado -->
  <div
    class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[70vh] md:h-[80vh] text-white px-4 py-12"
  >
    <p
      class="text-yellow-400 text-sm md:text-base mb-2 tracking-[0.4em] opacity-0 animate-fade-in-up [animation-delay:200ms]"
    >
      DESDE 2005
    </p>

    <h1
      class="text-white text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-8xl font-black mb-4 md:mb-8 leading-tight tracking-tight text-center opacity-0 animate-fade-in-up [animation-delay:400ms]"
    >
      El arte <br />
      <span class="italic font-normal">del Corte</span>
    </h1>

    <div
      class="w-24 h-1 bg-yellow-400 mb-6 opacity-0 animate-fade-in-up [animation-delay:500ms]"
    >
    </div>

    <p
      class="mt-2 md:mt-4 text-sm md:text-xl text-center max-w-2xl drop-shadow-lg px-4 leading-relaxed opacity-0 animate-fade-in-up [animation-delay:600ms]"
    >
      Experimente la excelencia de la maduración en seco. Cada filete es una
      obra maestra, seleccionado a mano y madurado durante 45 días.
    </p>

    <!-- Botones lado a lado en desktop, apilados en móvil -->
    <div
      class="mt-10 md:mt-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 w-full md:w-auto px-4 md:px-0 opacity-0 animate-fade-in-up [animation-delay:800ms]"
    >
      <a
        href="#prices"
        class="shimmer-btn bg-yellow-400 px-8 py-4 rounded hover:bg-yellow-500 text-black font-black tracking-widest text-sm text-center transition-all"
      >
        EXPLORAR EL MENÚ
      </a>

      <a
        href="#galeria"
        class="bg-transparent border border-white/30 px-8 py-4 rounded hover:bg-white hover:text-black font-black tracking-widest text-sm text-center transition-all"
      >
        VER GALERÍA
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
